      <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-primary/5 to-secondary/5 p-6 rounded-box border border-primary/20 backdrop-blur-sm">
        <h4 class="font-semibold text-primary mb-3">Sovereignty Assessment Checklist:</h4>
        <ul class="text-base-content/70 text-sm space-y-2">
          <li>• <strong class="text-primary">Financial:</strong> Could you survive 12+ months without your current income?</li>
          <li>• <strong class="text-primary">Professional:</strong> Could you find equivalent work in 90 days if needed?</li>
          <li>• <strong class="text-primary">Emotional:</strong> Is your self-worth independent of others' opinions?</li>
          <li>• <strong class="text-primary">Social:</strong> Would you still have close relationships if one group rejected you?</li>
          <li>• <strong class="text-primary">Geographic:</strong> Could you relocate within 6 months if opportunity or necessity arose?</li>
          <li>• <strong class="text-primary">Identity:</strong> Do you have fulfillment from multiple sources, not just one role?</li>
